\begin_layout Definition
The regression line with intercept equals to zero, i.e., for 
\begin_inset Formula $i=1,2,\ldots,n.$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{i}=\beta_{1}x_{i}+\epsilon_{i}
\]

\end_inset

 is often called the regression through the origin model.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
